reviewText: The series was just as advertised....beautiful color, no skips, good shape when delivered and enjoyed by family immensely.
The disc all skip every time I get into a movie it won't play I have to reload the disc and start over every time it gets to the same spot the episode will not play
I spent $30 per season of little house for 9 seasons! This Less than $100 for all 9 seasons! A great deal! It is such a family friendly, educational and fun series! My favorite tv show of all times!!
I loved finding this item! Its got a great little house to store the discs in.
I wish that the price was $49.99 or $59.99 with free shipping
